text: Colobothea nigromaculata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Dmytro Zajciw in 1971. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Colobothea nigromaculata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1971
